title: Record book of the Iowa Ornithologists' Association
contributing_institution: Iowa State University. Special Collections and University Archives
creator: Iowa Ornithological Association
contributor: Bartsch, Paul, 1871-1960;Merriam, C. Hart (Clinton Hart), 1855-1942;Currier, Edmonde S.;Giddings, Harold Joseph;Henning, Carl Fritz;Hoover, George C.;Rich, Guy C.;Savage, David L.;Bailey, Bert Heald;Heaton, Hiram;Irons, Ernest E. (Ernest Edward), 1877-;Law, John Eugene, 1877-1931;Goss, R. D.
description: Record book for the Iowa Ornithological Association. The book covers the period from the group's founding as the Iowa Ornithologist's Association on June 15, 1894 to January 16, 1898. The record book includes meeting minutes, copies of the organization's constitution, financial reports, officer and membership lists, and letters regarding the Iowa Ornithological Association.
subject: Ornithology--Societies, etc;Meetings;Societies--History, organization, etc.
